Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 89 Whitfield Street is the last available unit in the market leading 80 Charlotte Street development. With a private entrance and dual frontage on Whitfield Street and Howland Street, the office space will make a distinctive, self-contained home for any aspirational modern business. With its 4,090 sq ft floorplate and 2.9m ceiling heights, the contemporary, open-plan space, offers flexible layout options and an uplifting sense of spaciousness. The large, openable windows provide abundant light and fresh air for an enhanced working environment. As part of the 80 Charlotte Street development there are additional benefits including access to comprehensive end of journey facilities, communal 2,950 sq ft roof terrace and bar / cafe.
